<cl=A2A2A2>
The Thieves guild is as old as the very world of Sphere. Although ambitious Thieves demand both a high title and degree to achieve success in the guild, they are nonetheless not interested in the pure magic of elements, but prefer alchemy as more useful in their profession. Success in the world of thieves by no means contributes to endurance, but the dexterity and accuracy of Thieves remain unmatched. The Guild's secret skills are the subject of the envy of many, as Thieves have penetrated into the mystery of invisibility without any magical rings or amulets.
<br>
